Global Capital Projects Consulting Market Insights
Capital Projects Consulting Market size was valued at USD 12.34 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 18.50 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.85% from 2024 to 2030.

Capital Projects Consulting Market Overview
The global Capital Projects Consulting market size was valued at approximately USD 15.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.3% during the forecast period. The market includes services provided by consultants in areas such as construction project management, planning, procurement, and design, primarily for large-scale infrastructure, industrial, and commercial developments. Increasing investment in infrastructure projects, urbanization, and demand for sustainable construction are driving this market's growth. Additionally, the need for expert guidance in risk management, cost estimation, and project delivery timelines further fuels demand for consulting services.

